uqbel a d-yedṛu wannect-a, kunwi s inelmaden-iw a d-yebdu leɛtab di tegniț n ccedda : ur tezmirem ara aț-țeččeḍ aț-țwaɣeḍ d wid iḥekkmen deg iman-nsen, ț-țcafɛem iman-nsen, tbeddeḍ ɣef yiman-nsen, tbeddleḍ, tbeddleḍ ɣer webrid, tbeddleḍ ɣef waṭas n lɛaddat-nsen.
Exdem lmeǧhud-ik iwakken ur tețɛeṭṭileḍ ara a d-taseḍ ɣuṛ-es, tețqellib amek ara k-n-yawi ț-ținezduɣt-ik ?
Lameɛna igellil ilaq ad iqleɛ iman-ik s wul yeṣfan,
Imi teṭṭfeḍ deg awal-ik s wul yeṣfan, tjeṛbeḍ di teṛwiḥt-agi,, tessawḍem acḥal bɣiɣ a d-terrem ddehn nwen ɣuṛ-ek ɣer tama nniḍen. Lameɛna asm'ara tuɣaleḍ d iɣed !
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer tsirtirt n wuzzal deg yiwet n tɣuṛfeț, igṭaṭṭaṭ ( lehwa ) d ixeddamen n lbabuṛ ; syenna qebblen abrid-nsen ɣer tmurt n Asya iṛuḥ ɣef tmura n Asya d Iberdan.
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer tsirtirt n temdint n Ludikus, ifka-yi-d ɣef lexṣaṣ, ɣeṛɣeṛ-ed tlata kilumitrat ger watmaten-iw n tmurt n Asya di lexṣaṣ.
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tɣawsiwin nniḍen i gețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, țțawil-ik si mkul tama ɣer tmurt n Asya mačči d nekk yellan di ddunit.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tzemmurt n lɛali ɣas akken d aḥeccad i telliḍ, acḥal ihi i sen-ishel i nutni yellan ț-țiṣeḍwa n tzemmurt iwakken ad uɣalen ad țțuleqmen ɣef tzemmurt-nneɣ.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed meyya n lɣellat, mkul agur tețțak-ed lfakya. Iferrawen-is d ddwa yesseḥlayen leǧnas.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n lqanun s ɣuṛ Qayṣeṛ ameqqran ; yefka lameṛ a d-yawi si tmurt n Selyan nețța ț-țigzirt n Jlili, si tmurt n Selyan nețța ț-țilawin-nsen d asfel, wid akk yumnen s Lmasiḥ, ilaq ad iṛuḥ a d-yawi waḍu ɣer wemkan n ddunit.
A lḥakem ameqqran ! S uḍebbaṛ-ik yelhan i d-yers lxiṛ d lehna ɣef tmurt-agi ! Ɣef wayagi, a Filiks ameqqran, ncekkeṛ-ik meṛṛa di mkul amkan ;
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurtnur, aɛessas n tmes yellan di temdint n Haranya yellan di tmurt n Azerbaz, armi ț-țigzirt n Qubṛus ț-țemdint n temdint n Lquds.
Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg yiwen.
Tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, yețnerni di tmurt n Jlili, yuɣal dedṛani di mkul amkan anda llant ccwal.
Tamdint-agi, terɛeḍ, tezzenz-it amenzu, yuɣal-ed ɣer tewwurt n temdint n Amasya.
Di yal tama n tmurt slan s wannect-agi, țergigin i wasif n Lufrat. Yesɣeṛ asif-nni iwakken a sen-yefk tamurt-nni i lejdud-nneɣ.
Nufa dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef temdint n Tyatir, isem-is Frij. Llant gar-aneɣ azal n xemsa yirrijemmaḍ n tegzirt n Kritus.
Deg umkan-agi iqedsen yella yiwen n leḥjab ifeṛqen amkan iqedsen d umkan iqedsen nezzeh,
Di yal tamdint i deg ɛeddan, țxebbiṛen atmaten s lewṣayat yellan di tebṛaț i d-fkan lbabuṛ, nehhu akk-d țmurt n tmes i grennu.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Di leǧwahi-nni, llan i tmura n ifariziyen i d-yusan si tmurt n Jlili, si tmurt n Switzerland, llan kra nniḍen dinna wid n tegzirt n Qubṛus, d wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ. Meɛna m'ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen, ilaq ad immeslayen deg-sen ur ilaq ara a t-nemmeslayen deg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen.
Di tejmaɛt n temdint n Antyuc llan kra n tmura ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail axaṭer llan kra n yemdanen seg wid i d-yerɣalen di tmurt n Galasya, di tmurt n Ssyadiyen ț-țmurt-agi i d-yețwaceggɛen ɣuṛ-es eɛlayen, ițbeggin-ed tideț n Sidi Ṛebbi s waṭas n lecɣal i d-yemmeslayen.
Di yal amkan n tmurt n Frijya akk-d Skuwiyen, țxebbiṛent-ed s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, rnan-d wid yesselmaden si tejmaɛt n ifariziyen, rnan-d daɣen wid yesɛan tazmert ad slemṛen fell-ak, ilaq aț-țiliḍ d lemtel.
nɛedda seddaw yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, isem-is Xelɛa ț-țezmert.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lebḥuṛ akk-d wid yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, țțawint si tmanyin ar meyya uɛecrin n litrat, seg-sent i d-țɛemmiṛen di lebḥur, deg waggur-nsent di luḍu.
Akken yella Bulus yețdafaɛ ɣef yiman-is, qṛib a d-yawi Britanya, ɣer temdint n Sban, iwakken aț-țemfaṛaqem ɣer mkul tama, ur țțafen ara ayen n diri ara yilin yid-es s tdukli iwakken a t-yessiweḍ lexbaṛ.
Sɛut iles aẓidan, llan gar-asen ayen ur nezmir ara a t-sxedɛen ; aț-țilim d lemtel i yemcumen-agi neɣ i wid yețxalafen iman-nsen.
S tutlayin-agi i d-yusan s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara, am akken i țɛicin s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, am akken i tella di tutlayt ur nețwassen ara.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-nsen a s-tṛuḥ.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d waman nniḍen.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg iḍ, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. M'ara yili d sebba n tuccḍa n wiyaḍ, ma d win ara ikecmen ɣer daxel, ad ccwaḍu d iḍuṛṛen.
M'ara kkun-ẓẓuɣṛen a kkun awin ɣer ccṛeɛ, ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud-nwen ; ma yella wamek, a d-yaweḍ wass n westeɛfu !
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tzemmurt n lɛali ɣas akken d aḥeccad i telliḍ, acḥal ihi i sen-ishel i nutni yellan ț-țiṣeḍwa n tzemmurt iwakken ad uɣalen ad țțuleqmen ɣef tzemmurt-nsen.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, ur țsetḥin ara s uweḥḥi-nsen meɛna ɣuṛ-sen i ten-ițṛaǧun.
?ef wannect-agi, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt akteṛ n temdinin n ?ur d Sidun.
Aɛeqqa-yagi d nețța i d amecṭuḥ meṛṛa ger zzerriɛat yellan, lameɛna mi gețwazreɛ, igemmu yețțali alamma yekka-d sennig akk yemɣan n tebḥirt.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a ț-mmeslayen deg waṭas n temẓi nniḍen, yerna nnuba-ten, yerna nqudeṛ-iten, aṭas deg-sen i gemmuten.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n lmut.
Amur nniḍen n zzerriɛa yeɣli ger yedɣaɣen , mi d-temɣi teqquṛ imi xuṣṣen waman.
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n ccṛeɛ ;
Llan deg-s lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n mkul ṣṣifa, wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, akk-d yefṛax n igenni s mkul ṣṣifa, akk-d leḍyuṛ-nsen s mkul ṣṣenf, ur d-ssufuɣen ara tikufɛen seg-s.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, axaṭer tafaweț-nni tajḍiṭ aț-țejbed aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim, acerrig-nni ad innerni.
